guidelines: {"blocks":[{"key":"bthju","text":"The BioBrick® Assembly Kit provides a streamlined method for assembly of BioBrick parts into multi-component genetic systems. BioBrick parts are DNA sequences that encode a defined biological function and can be readily assembled with any other BioBrick part. The process for assembling any two BioBrick parts is identical and results in a new composite BioBrick part.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"sup","offset":12,"length":1}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bnqne","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aao9h","text":"The BioBrick Assembly Kit contains EcoRI-HF®, XbaI, SpeI, PstI, T4 DNA Ligase and NEBuffer 2.1.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"sup","offset":43,"length":1}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7l4on","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"bbf66","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7lcgu","text":"BioBrick Assembly Overview","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"imageblock","mutability":"","data":{"guid":"918B9B895F7C48F3B5F140E1717BA230","height":null,"is_video":false,"mime":null,"original_name":null,"placeholder":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","source":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":null}}}}
